# OpenCode Local Rules (machine-specific, not committed to this public repo)

Copy this file to `AGENTS.local.md` in the same directory and fill in your
own machine-specific pointers. `AGENTS.local.md` is git-ignored; its content
is appended after the public `global_rules.md` when OpenCode's `AGENTS.md` is
built during Home Manager activation.

## Memory

- `<path-to-your-personal-context-repo>` is the canonical store for durable
  personal context, knowledge, decisions, and progress logs. Before
  non-trivial personal, research, learning, or career work, read its entry
  file and follow its index files.
